# Starlight docs (`apps/docs-app`)

## Content paths

- Documentation pages live under `apps/docs-app/src/content/docs/`.
- Each sidebar `autogenerate` directory should have an `index.md` with frontmatter `title`.

## Authoring

- Prefer clear headings: Overview → Prerequisites → Procedures → Next steps.
- Avoid bare angle-bracket placeholders in MDX if they can be parsed as JSX; use backticks or escapes per Starlight guidance.

## Links

- Link to Engineering Standard (`docs/ENGINEERING_STANDARD.md` in the templates root) for normative rules; keep docs in sync when rules change.
